      { :title => "You're Never Too Young To Be Charitable", :teaser => nil, :text => "<p>\r\n\t\tAt Share Your Wish, we believe that teaching our children the virtues of generosity and selflessness by helping others is of utmost importance.  We believe it gives them a sense of empowerment, and respect for others that they will take with them for the rest of their lives.  We want the spirit of giving to be a way of life for our children, and even make it a habit.  And we don't believe it's ever too soon.  By raising individuals who learn to appreciate what they have, while understanding that not everyone is as fortunate, we hope to create a better world for generations to come.  While there are unlimited ways to accomplish this, here is our Top 10 List...\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t10.  Donate...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tGo shopping with your child and have them select a toy for a child who may not be as fortunate.  Before you shop, find a charity you would like to donate the toy to and tell your child about that charity.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t9.  Spring cleaning all year round...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tClean out closets and donate the clothes to a local charity in your neighborhood.  Tell your child that the clothes that don't fit them anymore can go to a child who needs them.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t8. For sale...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tMake a lemonade stand or start a bake sale and donate some or all of the money to a charity.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t7.  Kindness Counts...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tKeep a kindness chart and keep track of the wonderful thing your family does to give back to others.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t6.   Watch it...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tBe a role model for your children.  Practice what you preach.  Share ways you give back to others.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t5.  Get involved...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tOrganize an event in your community that focuses on giving back to others.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t4.  Volunteer...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tVolunteer to lend a hand to an organization and get your whole family involved.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t3.   Family First...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tRemind your children that family will always be more important than things.  After a fun family day talk about how much fun it was spending time together.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t2.  Teach, Share, Inspire...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tYour friends and family to do the same things you are doing at home.  Kindness is contagious.\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<br />\r\n\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t1.  Share Your Wish...\r\n\t\t<div class=\"indent-me\">\r\n\t\t\tUse www.shareyourwish.com when planning your child's next birthday party.  Our website is designed to help children give back and learn the true meaning of celebration!\r\n\t\t</div>", :slug => "learn/teach", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false },
      { :title => "How It Works - Overview", :teaser => nil, :text => "How It Works text", :slug => "how-it-works", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false},
      { :title => "How ShareYourWish Works - For the Host", :teaser => nil, :text => "<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">1</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">CREATE YOUR EVENT PAGE</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Register your child's birthday details</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Personalize the page</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step1.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">2</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">SELECT A CHARITY TO SUPPORT</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Choose up to three (3) charities</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Choose a Donation Level - contributions will be split between a Gift Fund and a Donation Fund</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step2.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">3</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">INVITE GUESTS TO PARTICIPATE</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Guests receive an email invitation</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>No need to shop!</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>No need to guess about a gift!</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Contributions can be made anonymously</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step3.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">4</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">YOUR GIFTS ARE SHARED</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Use the Gift Fund to buy a meaningful gift from our partner Amazon.com</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>We'll process the Donation Fund to your charities in your child's name</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step4.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">5</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">HAVE A GREAT PARTY</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Bring the special gift and our reward certificate to the party</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Add Goodies for extra learning and celebration</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>We'll help you recognize and thank Guests for sharing too</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step5.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"how-step-row\">\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-num\">6</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-description\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"how-step-title\">MAKE THE WORLD A LITTLE BETTER</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Share your experience and tips to help the Share Your Wish community</li>\r\n\t\t\t<li>Inspire friends and family to Share Their Wish</li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"how-step-image\">\r\n\t\t<%= image_tag 'how-it-works/step6.jpg' %>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>", :slug => "how-it-works/for-the-host", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false },
      { :title => "How ShareYourWish Works - For the Guest", :teaser => nil, :text => "<ol class=\"how-it-works-list\">\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tReceive email invitation to participate in Share Your Wish from host of the party. Follow the link in your email to the event page.\r\n\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tAlternatively, log onto ShareYourWish.com and search for the party by the Child's name. Use the \"Magic Phrase\" provided to you by the event's Host to gain access\r\n\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tChoose the amount of gift (anonymous unless otherwise requested) that you would like to make to the birthday boy/girl\r\n\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tAll gifts from guests are aggregated and delivered to birthday boy/girl.  They then donate a portion of those gifts to a charity(s) of their choice, and a meaningful gift on behalf of all guests is purchased with the remainder\r\n\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tFeel good! You've helped somebody to share their wish by helping others!\r\n\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\tHopefully you are inspired to continue to teach, share, and inspire yourself\r\n\t</ol>\r\n", :slug => "how-it-works/for-the-guest", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false },
      { :title => "How ShareYourWish Works - FAQ", :teaser => nil, :text => "How ShareYourWish Works - FAQ text", :slug => "how-it-works/faq", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false },
      { :title => "Browse - Overview", :teaser => nil, :text => "Browse - Overview text", :slug => "browse", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false},
      { :title => "Browse - Award Wall", :teaser => nil, :text => "Browse - Award Wall text", :slug => "browse/award-wall", :order => 0, :show_in_menu => false }
    ]) unless Page.count > 0
  end

  def down
    Page.destroy_all
